Smart fountain operation example:
If you want to control the fountain, you can say "Alexa, ask fresco turn on fountain." fountain is the name of the device name; you can see the device name in the Fresco Pro app;
If you want to turn off the smart fountain's LED indicator, you can say "Alexa, ask fresco turn off the LED of fountain";
If you want to know the water level, you can say "Alexa, ask fresco what is the water level of the fountain?",
To know TDS value, you can say "Alexa, ask fresco what is the TDS value of the fountain?"
